Carrefour to Continue Seeking Brazil Opportunities, Olofsson Tells Estado

-- B y   F r a n c i s c o   M a r c e l i n o
-- 
2011-07-15T10:15:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/carrefour-to-continue-seeking-brazil-opportunities-olofsson-tells-estado.html
Carrefour SA (CA)  will continue seeking
growth opportunities in  Brazil  after a proposal to merge with
Cia. Brasileira de Distribuicao Grupo Pao de Acucar failed, O
Estado de S. Paulo reported, citing an e-mailed interview with
ChairmanLars Olofsson.  Carrefour doesn’t plan to sell its unit in Brazil after the
proposal by the Gama fund lost the support of the nation’s state
development bank BNDES, Olofsson told the  newspaper .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francisco Marcelino in  Sao Paulo  at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Laura Price at 
 lprice3@bloomberg.net  